{"type": "article", "id": 29067, "title": "混凝土时钟", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-04T05:10:57Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160704024450DVwlFAmWfs0ev461.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">法国艺术家和设计师 Bertrand Jayr 最近为 Lyon Béton 用混凝土打造了一系列极简而美观的家饰，今天介绍的 Life in Progress 时钟就是其中的一款产品。光滑的钟面上并没有作任何数字标示，仅通过两根指针和十二个缺口表现时间。它不仅能够简单地放置在任何平面，内置的四根铝尺允许你随意地将它悬挂在墙上。这是它的<a href=\"http://us.lyon-beton.com/store/concrete-accessories/life-in-progress-clock/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 123 美元。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024535kfUSVleF7PIBcQCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024556wEQbIByzc10TsqG8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.571429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607040246159kJreaPUwo7Q8jn4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160704024637ws8YJTLgZD2BihUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}